The Minister for Finance and Planning, Dr Philip Mpango said the government revenue collection is abided by set rules and regulations. All TRA staff (a few of them) who engaging in such kind of practice should stop immediately. Traders name to us those who engaged in those practice, Dr Mpango said when tabling 2017/18 nation budget today.He condemned tax collection using force, abuse language, overtaxing traders and bride soliciting and ordered all those practice to stop.In 2017/18 the government wants to increase of domestic revenue collections to 16.5percent of GDP and increase tax revenue collection to 14.2 percent of GDP.